"pid":"6575e0a31f26099592d5ca5642f3715e06a26b26","tid":1252744,"uid":35842,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:48:35.000Z","msg":"[本地]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今晚</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5fOn5Xz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5fOn5Xz.png&h=93d52169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[本地]星期三(26號）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAoZ8Qc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAoZ8Qc.png&h=f0dedb4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[澳洲 ~ Melb]星期三(26號）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffqedhH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FffqedhH.png&h=a989d4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">顧題驚呼，主問何事，吾宣讀之，題讀畢，文尚未讀，主已面白，自語喃喃，狂嚎「共慘黨殺到，香港九龍新界無得避，余要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生...共慘黨殺到，香港九龍新界無得避，余要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘黨殺到，香港九龍新界無得避，余要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n話音未落，直登樓頂，大嚷&quot;鳴呀，我便何如?&quot;即一躍而下，眾人追，亦不及，二女僕見即驚倒，尚有男僕驚至失神，不停詢眾索腸蛋裹腹。<br />\n<br />\n余幸保清健，但見同室五十餘僕旋即斷炊，如此王八，害人不淺&hellip;&hellip;</span>"},{"pid":"4c3df0b1035ba7f55d9d1c0222acd655cc64efb6","tid":1252744,"uid":141131,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"呼籲千奇唔好取消戶口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留低少過60 蚊，咁樣相關系統就會觸動最低存款額下限，要求戶口持有人增加存款額，以及扣手續費，但唔夠$60，又扣唔到你數<br />\n<br />\n咁又會多咗一條扣數不成嘅 Error Tranx，又要額外處理<br />\n<br />\n佢就要出幾封信俾你，增加咗人手同郵件物成本"},{"pid":"9011f3fb46328f039598012e759b8863a6c652a7","tid":1252744,"uid":5701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco